snippet.title: Project Haven | OTK Games Expo 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Gameplay trailer showcased on OTK Games Expo 2023.

Project Haven brings a gritty dystopian story, along with the intricate mechanics of the classics, to the Tactical Turn-Based genre.
Wishlist on Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/443190/Project_Haven/

You can get the latest news and be part of our development process through our social media:
Discord: https://discord.gg/fFMd8FU​

Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/ProjectHaven...
